beer.beer_description:
When you grow up on black and gold, you never forget those colours. And when you grow up in the area, you never truly leave. 

Drink west lager pairs perfectly with a fresh pair of TN's and tall stories about how your old man nearly played for Pennies. 

It's as refreshing as an empty train to the city in peak hour, and as crisp as the Kingsway in winter. 

This is the beer from Western Sydney.

Like anything good, this beer is a product of the west 
This beer is for those who remember where they came from. This beer is for those they called Westies, fibros, squinters. The working men and women.
And the west doesn't end anywhere. Every city has a west. Every town has a west. West begins at the harbour bridge. It goes from Parra to Perth. Whoever you are, we'll have you.
